svg.text: Complete the exercise below to check your understanding of what you learned in Section 3.
If you have questions, consult the Language Reference section.
Use the words in the list on the left to complete each sentence below.
他说，我们可以明天去买衣服。
When a word is made of two (or more) characters, the meaning of the word is
often a combination of the meanings of the separate characters. Based on the
characters you’ve learned, try to match each unfamiliar word to its meaning.
